WEBVTT

00:00.228 --> 00:01.974
There is a revolution coming.

00:02.709 --> 00:04.641
Excuse me, what do you mean?

00:05.020 --> 00:10.295
The future is staring back at us like a perfect picture on glass...

00:11.418 --> 00:13.845
...and this future, it must be protected.

00:14.137 --> 00:15.663
But what's it got to do with me?

00:15.779 --> 00:16.537
Look.

00:18.268 --> 00:19.023
What is it?

00:19.179 --> 00:20.944
It will change everything.

00:22.638 --> 00:24.659
That's why they want to stop it.

00:25.494 --> 00:28.040
They will come after you without cease...

00:28.980 --> 00:33.803
...because the future belongs to us.

00:39.692 --> 00:42.800
LG OLED: perfect picture on glass.

00:48.185 --> 00:48.781
Who are you?

00:49.491 --> 00:52.227
Oh, come now, I've already told you.

00:52.439 --> 00:54.804
The future is staring back at you.

00:57.263 --> 00:59.376
LG OLED TV.

